<h2>Steps :</h2>
<ul>
<li>F2L : First two layers</li>
<li>First layer cross : Draw a cross on a face of your choice. Make sure that the 4 edges are in front of the center of the right color.</li>
<li>First layer corner : Once you drew a cross, add the 3 corners. That's right, only 3, leave one corner empty. Make sure once again that each corner is at the right place.</li>
<li>Now you should have one completed face with the first crowd (still missing one corner)</li>
<li>Hold the cube with the face you almost completed facing down</li>
<li>Move the down layer (D and D') until the empty corner is under the edge of the second layer you want to place</li>
<li>Move the top layer (U and U') until the edge you want to place is above its place. Make sure that the color facing you is above its center</li>
<li>Place it algo</li>
<li>Repeat untill you have the second layer almost finished.</li>
<li>Now, place the last missing corner at its place. Be careful not to mess the 75% completed second layer.</li>
<li>Nom, place the last missing edge above its place, the color facing you matching the color it's above of.</li>
<li>algo</li>
<li>You now have 2 layers done.</li>
<li>Now build the last layer (referred as the Yellow layer) cross.</li>
<li>algos</li>
<li>Now orient each corner(OLL)</li>
<li>Now place each corner (bedroom technic)</li>
<li>Now place each edges (PLL)</li>
</ul>

